milestones.description: Dean Minors and Romaine's 98-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 65 between Romaine and Gibbons
Leverock has become the top wicket-taker for BMUDA in ODIs with 11 wickets, going past O'Brien's 10
This is the highest match aggregate (506) involving teams Bermuda & Kenya in ODIs
Dean Minors and Romaine's 98-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 68 between Romaine and Clay Smith
Mukuddem has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for BMUDA, going past Romaine
